@startuml
title Abstract Factory - Ejemplo 3 - solucion para familias de vehiculos
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  interface Car <<interfaz>> {
  }
  class Catalog {
    +showFamily(): void
  }
  class ElectricCar {
    +specs(): String
  }
  class ElectricScooter {
    +specs(): String
  }
  class ElectricVehicleFactory {
    +createScooter(): Scooter
    +createCar(): Car
  }
  class GasCar {
    +specs(): String
  }
  class GasScooter {
    +specs(): String
  }
  class GasVehicleFactory {
    +createScooter(): Scooter
    +createCar(): Car
  }
  interface Scooter <<interfaz>> {
  }
  interface VehicleFactory <<interfaz>> {
  }
}

Car <|.. ElectricCar
Scooter <|.. ElectricScooter
VehicleFactory <|.. ElectricVehicleFactory
Car <|.. GasCar
Scooter <|.. GasScooter
VehicleFactory <|.. GasVehicleFactory
Car ..> GasScooter : crea
Car ..> ElectricCar : crea
Car ..> ElectricScooter : crea
Car ..> GasCar : crea
Catalog ..> GasScooter : crea
Catalog ..> ElectricCar : crea
Catalog ..> ElectricScooter : crea
Catalog ..> GasCar : crea
ElectricCar ..> GasScooter : crea
ElectricCar ..> ElectricScooter : crea
ElectricCar ..> GasCar : crea
ElectricScooter ..> GasScooter : crea
ElectricScooter ..> ElectricCar : crea
ElectricScooter ..> GasCar : crea
ElectricVehicleFactory ..> GasScooter : crea
ElectricVehicleFactory ..> ElectricCar : crea
ElectricVehicleFactory ..> ElectricScooter : crea
ElectricVehicleFactory ..> GasCar : crea
GasCar ..> GasScooter : crea
GasScooter ..> GasCar : crea
GasVehicleFactory ..> GasScooter : crea
GasVehicleFactory ..> GasCar : crea
Scooter ..> GasScooter : crea
Scooter ..> ElectricCar : crea
Scooter ..> ElectricScooter : crea
Scooter ..> GasCar : crea
VehicleFactory ..> GasScooter : crea
VehicleFactory ..> ElectricCar : crea
VehicleFactory ..> ElectricScooter : crea
VehicleFactory ..> GasCar : crea
Main ..> Catalog : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
